title: Kemono Friends: Youkoso Japari Park e!
original_name: けものフレンズ ようこそジャパリパークへ！
sinopse: Since childhood Nana has been dreaming of becoming a caretaker at the Japari Park, all because "Friends," unique human-like animals, live there. And today her dream finally came true! But will she be able to earn their trust?
